## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="4e401-102"><xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsView>控制會引發<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsView.PageIndexChanging>事件的頁面巡覽區按鈕時 (按鈕，以使用其`CommandName`屬性設定為 「 頁面 」) 在控制項內按一下時，之前<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsView>控制項處理分頁作業。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4e401-102">The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsView> control raises the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsView.PageIndexChanging> event when a pager button (a button with its `CommandName` property set to "Page") within the control is clicked, but before the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsView> control handles the paging operation.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4e401-103">這可讓您提供執行自訂的常式，例如取消分頁作業，每次這個事件發生時的事件處理常式。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4e401-103">This allows you to provide an event handler that performs a custom routine, such as canceling the paging operation, whenever this event occurs.</span></span>  
  
> [!NOTE]
>  <span data-ttu-id="4e401-104">頁面巡覽區按鈕通常位於中的頁面巡覽列<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsView>控制項。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4e401-104">Pager buttons are usually located in the pager row of a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsView> control.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="4e401-105">A<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsViewPageEventArgs>物件會傳遞至事件處理常式，可讓您判斷使用者所選頁面的索引，並指出是否應該取消分頁作業。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4e401-105">A <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsViewPageEventArgs> object is passed to the event handler, which allows you to determine the index of the page selected by the user and to indicate whether the paging operation should be canceled.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4e401-106">若要判斷使用者所選頁面的索引，請使用<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsViewPageEventArgs.NewPageIndex%2A>屬性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4e401-106">To determine the index of the page selected by the user, use the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsViewPageEventArgs.NewPageIndex%2A> property.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4e401-107">若要取消分頁作業，請設定<xref:System.ComponentModel.CancelEventArgs.Cancel%2A>的屬性<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsViewPageEventArgs>物件到`true`。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4e401-107">To cancel the paging operation, set the <xref:System.ComponentModel.CancelEventArgs.Cancel%2A> property of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsViewPageEventArgs> object to `true`.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="4e401-108">如需如何處理事件的詳細資訊，請參閱[處理和引發事件](~/docs/standard/events/index.md)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4e401-108">For more information about how to handle events, see [Handling and Raising Events](~/docs/standard/events/index.md).</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="4e401-109">如需 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsViewPageEventArgs> 類別之執行個體的初始屬性值清單，請參閱 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsViewPageEventArgs.%23ctor%2A> 建構函式。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4e401-109">For a list of initial property values for an instance of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsViewPageEventArgs> class, see the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsViewPageEventArgs.%23ctor%2A> constructor.</span></span>  
  
   
  
